post001.title: This Would be the Oldest Post
post001.author: OC Radio Staff
post001.body: OC Radio is currently being built from the ground up by students at Olympic College. See our plans for the future in the news section, check the calendar for current events, or contact us to learn more. P.S. Don't be afraid to volunteer, we meet Friday's at 10am in TEC 114. We hope to see you there.
